    "en": {
      "title": "A young man was arrested with cannabis in the presidential palace",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Special Task Force says that a 24-year-old resident of Mirigama was arrested with a small parcel containing cannabis inside the President's House in Colombo.",
        "When checking a person who was behaving suspiciously near the swimming pool of the President's House, this parcel containing ganja was found in his possession.",
        "The suspect is scheduled to be produced before the Fort Magistrate's Court today."
      ],
